// MediaRemoteConstants.def
//
// X-macro table of every NSString constant declared in MediaRemote.h.
// Each consumer #defines MR_NSSTRING(name) to its own expansion (extern decl,
// definition + fallback literal, or OSL_RESOLVE_NSSTRING call), #include's
// this file, then #undefs MR_NSSTRING.
//
// To add a new constant: add one line below in the appropriate section.
// To remove one: delete the line. The header, definitions, and constructor
// resolver list all stay in sync automatically.
//
// NOTE: This file lives next to MediaRemote.h in the SPM publicHeadersPath
// directory by design — MediaRemote.h #includes it via X-macro expansion to
// generate its extern declarations. Despite the public placement, this is
// NOT a standalone header: it has no header guard (re-include is required by
// the X-macro pattern) and #include-ing it without first defining
// MR_NSSTRING(name) will not produce useful output. Treat as internal.

// MARK: - Notifications
MR_NSSTRING(kMRMediaRemoteNowPlayingInfoDidChangeNotification)
